          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἁρπάζω</span></b> , fut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἁρπάξω</span>, aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἥρπαξα,
